{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"36a7c3da-7eae-4766-8f01-32d84dc7648b","content":"Here's the setup:\n\n**AppShell.xaml**\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<Shell x:Class=\"MyApp.AppShell\"\n       xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n       xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n       xmlns:views=\"clr-namespace:MyApp.Views\"\n       FlyoutBehavior=\"Flyout\">\n\n    <!-- Dashboard: single page in its own flyout item -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Dashboard\" Icon=\"dashboard.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:DashboardPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Products: two tabs (Active / Archived) -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Products\" Icon=\"products.png\">\n        <Tab Title=\"Active\">\n            <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ActiveProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n        <Tab Title=\"Archived\">\n            <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ArchivedProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Settings: separate flyout entry -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Settings\" Icon=\"settings.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:SettingsPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n</Shell>\n```\n\n**AppShell.xaml.cs** — register the detail route:\n```csharp\nnamespace MyApp;\n\npublic partial class AppShell : Shell\n{\n    public AppShell()\n    {\n        InitializeComponent();\n\n        // Register routes for pages not in the visual hierarchy\n        Routing.RegisterRoute(nameof(Views.ProductDetailsPage),\n                              typeof(Views.ProductDetailsPage));\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Navigating to the detail page** (e.g., from a list item tap):\n```csharp\nawait Shell.Current.GoToAsync($\"{nameof(ProductDetailsPage)}?id={product.Id}\");\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n| Element | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `FlyoutItem` | Top-level entry in the flyout menu |\n| `Tab` | Creates a bottom tab within a flyout item |\n| `ShellContent` | Wraps the actual page (lazy-loaded via `ContentTemplate`) |\n| `Routing.RegisterRoute` | Makes a page navigable by URI without placing it in the shell hierarchy |\n\nThe `Products` flyout item shows a bottom tab bar with \"Active\" and \"Archived\" when selected. `ProductDetailsPage` is pushed onto the navigation stack from either tab via the registered route.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d14f759b-6fb8-4c66-8a1c-8342ae4e8ad5","outputTokens":652,"requestId":"9427:1DC2AE:142BCE3:16826E2:6A066E80"},"id":"870d83e7-4cc6-4334-99ef-299b99923b22","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:53:31.794Z","parentId":"ab57618b-737b-408b-9185-68acd242ca15"}
